          The U.S. has <a href="https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/c5y46713z21o" target="_blank">confirmed</a> direct communication with Syria’s Hayat Tahrir al-Sham (HTS), a group designated as a terrorist organization due to its involvement in overturning the Assad regime. Secretary of State Antony Blinken said the talks were regarding the missing journalist Austin Tice. Blinken made these remarks in Jordan's safer meeting with other diplomats. He agrees that a peaceful transition and inclusive governance in Syria are essential to prevent chaos.</p>
